\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\",\"children\":2}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"掌握Swarm系统的架构设计\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2 text-gray-600\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\",\"children\":3}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"学会设计Agent之间的通信协议\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":1}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"开篇：从单Agent到Agent群体\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"单个Agent的能力有限，就像一个人面对复杂任务也会力不从心。\"}],\"$L13\"]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}],\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\"]}]}],\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$undefined\"]}],\"$L1c\"]}]]}]\n13:[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"Swarm（群智）让多个Agent协作，每个Agent专注自己的领域，共同完成复杂任务。\"}]\n14:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":2}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"什么是Agent Swarm？\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**Agent Swarm（群智）**是指多个自主Agent协作完成共同目标的系统。\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**类比**：\\n- 单Agent：一个超级专家，什么都做但可能不够专\\n- Swarm：多个专家团队，分工协作，更专业高效\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**Swarm的优势**：\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**1. 专业分工**\\n- Agent A：专注文档处理\\n- Agent B：专注数据分析\\n- Agent C：专注格式整理\\n- 各司其职，质量更高\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**2. 并行执行**\\n- 多个Agent同时工作\\n- 缩短总处理时间\\n- 资源利用率更高\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**3. 容错能力**\\n- 单个Agent失败不影响整体\\n- 自动重试和降级\\n- 系统更健壮\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**4. 可扩展性**\\n- 新增任务只需添加新Agent\\n- 不影响现有Agent\\n- 灵活适应变化\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"7\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**适用场景**：\\n- 复杂报告生成：调研Agent + 分析Agent + 写作Agent\\n- 多步骤工作流：采集Agent + 处理Agent + 存储Agent\\n- 代码开发：设计Agent + 编码Agent + 测试Agent + Review Agent\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-200\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-blue-900 font-medium\",\"children\":[\"💡 \",\"Swarm通过多个专业Agent的分工协作，实现比单Agent更强的能力和健壮性。\"]}]}]]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"div\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":3}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"Swarm架构模式\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**模式一：层级式（Hierarchical）**\\n```\\nManager Agent（管理者）\\n    ├→ Research Agent（研究员）\\n    ├→ Writer Agent（写作者）\\n    └→ Editor Agent（编辑者）\\n```\\n特点：有明确的指挥者，其他Agent执行指令。\\n适用：需要明确控制的场景。\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**模式二：去中心化（Decentralized）**\\n```\\nAgent A ⇄ Agent B ⇄ Agent C\\n   ↑        ↓\\nAgent D ⇄ Agent E ⇄ Agent F\\n```\\n特点：Agent之间平等协作，通过通信达成共识。\\n适用：需要灵活协调的场景。\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**模式三：流水线（Pipeline）**\\n```\\nAgent A → Agent B → Agent C → Agent D\\n  采集     处理     分析     输出\\n```\\n特点：按顺序传递数据，每个Agent处理一环。\\n适用：数据处理流程。\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**模式四：动态联盟（Dynamic Coalition）**\\n```\\n任务A: Agent A + Agent B\\n任务B: Agent B + Agent C + Agent E\\n任务C: Agent D + Agent F\\n```\\n特点：根据任务动态组建Agent团队。\\n适用：多任务并发的场景。\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"div\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":4}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"Agent通信协议\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**核心问题**：Agent之间如何交流？\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**协议要素**：\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**1. 消息格式**\\n```\\n{\\n  \\\"from\\\": \\\"agent_1\\\",\\n  \\\"to\\\": \\\"agent_2\\\",\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"request/acknowledge/result\\\",\\n  \\\"payload\\\": {...},\\n  \\\"timestamp\\\": 1234567890,\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"msg_123\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**2. 消息类型**\\n- Request：请求帮助\\n- Response：返回结果\\n- Acknowledge：确认收到\\n- Error：报告错误\\n- Broadcast：广播通知\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**3. 通信机制**\\n```\\n方式A：消息队列（推荐）\\n   所有Agent订阅队列\\n   通过队列异步通信\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"方式B：共享状态\\n   Agent读写共享数据结构\\n   适合强一致性场景\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"方式C：直接调用\\n   Agent之间函数调用\\n   同步但耦合度高\\n```\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"7\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**4. 冲突处理**\\n- 资源竞争：加锁机制\\n- 意见不一致：投票或仲裁\\n- 死锁：超时和回滚\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n1d:Tc39,from dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import List, Dict\nimport time\n\n@dataclass\nclass Message:\n    \"\"\"Agent消息\"\"\"\n    from_agent: str\n    to_agent: str\n    content: str\n    message_type: str = \"request\"\n\nclass Agent:\n    def __init__(self, name: str, role: str):\n        self.name = name\n        self.role = role\n        self.message_queue: List[Message] = []\n\n    def send_message(self, to_agent: 'Agent', content: str):\n        \"\"\"发送消息\"\"\"\n        msg = Message(\n            from_agent=self.name,\n            to_agent=to_agent.name,\n            content=content\n        )\n        to_agent.message_queue.append(msg)\n        print(f\"{self.name} → {to_agent.name}: {content[:30]}...\")\n\n    def process_messages(self) -> List[Message]:\n        \"\"\"处理消息\"\"\"\n        responses = []\n        while self.message_queue:\n            msg = self.message_queue.pop(0)\n            response = self.handle_message(msg)\n            if response:\n                responses.append(response)\n        return responses\n\n    def handle_message(self, msg: Message) -> Message | None:\n        \"\"\"处理消息（子类实现）\"\"\"\n        print(f\"{self.name} 收到: {msg.content[:30]}...\")\n        return None\n\nclass ResearchAgent(Agent):\n    def handle_message(self, msg: Message) -> Message:\n        \"\"\"研究员Agent：收集信息\"\"\"\n        if \"research\" in msg.content.lower():\n            result = f\"已完成关于{msg.content}的研究\"\n            return Message(\n                from_agent=self.name,\n                to_agent=msg.from_agent,\n                content=result\n            )\n        return super().handle_message(msg)\n\nclass WriterAgent(Agent):\n    def handle_message(self, msg: Message) -> Message:\n        \"\"\"写作者Agent：生成文档\"\"\"\n        if \"write\" in msg.content.lower():\n            result = f\"已根据{msg.content}生成文档\"\n            return Message(\n                from_agent=self.name,\n                to_agent=msg.from_agent,\n                content=result\n            )\n        return super().handle_message(msg)\n\nclass ManagerAgent(Agent):\n    \"\"\"管理者Agent：协调其他Agent\"\"\"\n    def __init__(self, name: str, agents: List[Agent]):\n        super().__init__(name, \"manager\")\n        self.agents = agents\n\n    def coordinate_task(self, task: str):\n        \"\"\"协调任务\"\"\"\n        print(f\"\n【{self.name}】分配任务: {task}\")\n\n        # 步骤1：指派研究Agent\n        research_agent = next(a for a in self.agents if a.role == \"researcher\")\n        self.send_message(research_agent, f\"请研究：{task}\")\n\n        # 模拟执行\n        research_agent.process_messages()\n\n        # 步骤2：指派写作者Agent\n        writer_agent = next(a for a in self.agents if a.role == \"writer\")\n        self.send_message(writer_agent, f\"请基于研究结果写文档\")\n\n        # 模拟执行\n        writer_agent.process_messages()\n\n# 创建Swarm\nresearch = ResearchAgent(\"ResearchBot\", \"researcher\")\nwriter = WriterAgent(\"WriterBot\", \"writer\")\nmanager = ManagerAgent(\"ManagerBot\", [research, writer])\n\n# 运行任务\nmanager.coordinate_task(\"AI技术发展趋势\")17:[\"$\",\"div\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":5}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"代码示例：简单的Swarm系统\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"实现一个层级式Swarm：\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-2 bg-gray-800 border-b border-gray-700\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-400 font-mono\",\"children\":\"python\"}]}],[\"$\",\"pre\",null,{\"className\":\"p-4 overflow-x-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-100 font-mono whitespace-pre\",\"children\":\"$1d\"}]}]]}],\"$undefined\"]}]\n18:[\"$\",\"div\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":6}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"实战：报告生成Swarm\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**场景**：自动生成行业研究报告\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**Swarm组成**：\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"1. **Manager Agent**\\n   - 接收用户需求\\n   - 分解任务\\n   - 协调各Agent\\n   - 汇总最终报告\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"2. **Research Agent**\\n   - 搜索最新资料\\n   - 提取关键信息\\n   - 整理数据\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"3. **Analysis Agent**\\n   - 分析数据趋势\\n   - 识别关键洞察\\n   - 发现问题机会\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"4. **Writing Agent**\\n   - 组织内容结构\\n   - 撰写各章节\\n   - 优化语言表达\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"5. **Review Agent**\\n   - 检查语法错误\\n   - 验证数据准确性\\n   - 评估整体质量\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"7\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**协作流程**：\\n```\\n用户 → Manager → Research (并行: 3个子任务）\\n                ↓\\n              Analysis (并行: 2个子任务）\\n                ↓\\n              Writing (串行：按章节顺序）\\n                ↓\\n              Review (检查+反馈）\\n                ↓\\n              Manager → 用户\\n```\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"8\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**优化点**：\\n- 并行执行子任务，缩短时间\\n- 设置超时，避免Agent卡住\\n- 质量阈值，Review不通过返工\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n19:[\"$\",\"div\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":7}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"Swarm挑战\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"Swarm系统复杂度高：Agent间通信延迟、协调逻辑复杂、调试困难、成本倍增。建议从简单场景开始，逐步扩展。\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-violet-50 rounded-xl border border-purple-200 p-6 mt-6\",\"childr